Day 8 — Pattern Problems (Logic Building)

Patterns are not about printing stars.
They train your brain to think in loops + conditions.

1. Basic Pattern
Example 1
*
* *
* * *
* * * *

Code:

for(int i = 1; i <= 4; i++){
    for(int j = 1; j <= i; j++){
        System.out.print("* ");
    }
    System.out.println();
}
Example 2
